{
  "stem": "7860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've seen first as a passenger train, which I used to ride daily.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would pull off to the side track.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody on the train knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A train load full of Jews in cattle cars heading in the direction of Treblinka and Majdanek, now to know where they were heading.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews would manage still to jump off the fast extreme moving trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you seen--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do not know how they managed to jump because each window-- each cattle car had two little windows.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the windows had barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On top of the rooftop would be manned by an Ukrainian, Estonian, a Lithuanian dressed in German uniform with machine gun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shoot anybody jumping out off the cattle car trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've seen with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I saw a cattle train pass by my passenger tried and go back onto the track.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And following the train who just passed us by, as we were riding the passenger train, I seen packs of men, and women, and children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Polish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Walking alongside the track capturing Jews who jumped off the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who are just managed limping alongside the tracks, laying dead, or is unconscious, or walking in daze.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And round them up with one German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would be accompanied by one German with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as they rounded them up, they made them dig a common grave, and take their clothes off first, so their clothes wouldn't get bloody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now I understand why they undressed them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the clothes would be a reward to the Poles who happened to round up these Jews who jumped off those first cattle cars heading to the direction of Treblinka and Majdanek from the direction of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've seen it myself many a times.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
